'''Wirzan''' nɣ '''Wawiḍlt''' nɣ '''Awjal''' nɣ '''Akujil''' (s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tnglizt]]: ''Lynx'') iga zɣ [[Amudr|imudar]] imsuṭṭaḍ imsksumn (lli icttan tifiyyi) d iga zɣ afrruy n [[Amuc|yimucciwn]].

Ar tlkkm taẓḍuyt n iwtman n uwjal gr 13 d 18 km, amma tiwtmin lli imẓẓin f iwtman ar lkkmnt 11 km. D immrwas ukujil kigan d ublinṣṛ, d ar yadlli ittuɣal mas dars kra n tzdayt mqquṛn d iblinṣṛn, macc ɣilad sslknnt tuzrawin n DNA nns mas ur tlli awd kra n tzdayt gratsn.

Ar tlkkm tiɣzi n wawiḍlt kra n 65 cm, d tɣzi n ucṭṭab nns gr 20 d 30 cm, d tattuyt nns dar iɣʷṛaḍ gr 40 cm d 45 cm. 

D sg tiɣawsiwin i bahra iẓllin wawiḍlt; imzgan nns isggann iɣzzifnin s kra n yizbaln n uglim iɣzzifnin ula nttni, d zdin d yimzgan ad ma ilkkmn kra n 20 n tgardat ar as ttaws g twafit n tirmt nns, amma izbaln n uglim ar as ttawsn ula nttni g ad issn ansa n ungisn nns.

